library(dplyr)
s <-                                                  #to create dataframe "s"
  n %>%                                                    #take dataframe "n"
group_by(Family) %>%                                        #Group it by Family

avgM = mean(Body_mass_male_mean, na.rm=TRUE))        #And mean female BM
